            <div class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-700 font-light">
              <p class="text-2xl text-deep-forest font-medium mb-6">
                Nestled in the heart of the Blue Ridge Mountains, Highlands, North Carolina, sits at an elevation of 4,118 feet, making it one of the highest incorporated towns east of the Mississippi.
              </p>

              <p class="mb-6">
                This mountain paradise isn't just known for its cool summer temperatures and vibrant fall foliage‚Äîit's home to some of the most spectacular waterfalls in the Southeast. The unique geography of the area, where the Blue Ridge Escarpment drops dramatically toward South Carolina, creates the perfect conditions for stunning cascades that draw visitors from around the world.
              </p>

              <div class="text-white rounded-xl p-8 my-12" style="background-color: rgb(71, 133, 169);">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">üèîÔ∏è Did You Know?</h3>
