              </div>

              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: rgb(71, 133, 169);">‚è∞ Time Planning</h3>
                <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
                  <div>
                    <strong>Dry Falls & Bridal Veil:</strong>
                    <br><span class="text-sm">Single morning, 45 min each</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <strong>Glen Falls:</strong>
                    <br><span class="text-sm">Afternoon adventure, 2+ hours</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <strong>Whitewater Falls:</strong>
                    <br><span class="text-sm">Half-day trip, 3+ hours total</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Conclusion -->
          <section class="mb-16">
            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: rgb(45, 69, 56);">The Magic of Mountain Water</h2>

              <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 font-light mb-6">
                These four waterfalls near Highlands, NC, each offer something unique‚Äîfrom the walk-behind wonder of Dry Falls to the drive-through novelty of Bridal Veil, from the triple cascade adventure of Glen Falls to the sheer majesty of Whitewater Falls.
